.idvancomycin
Antibiotic: Vancomycin
Indication: 
Duration: 
Dosing:
non-meningitis 10-15 mg/kg IV every 6-8h
meningitis 15 mg/kg IV q6h
Route: IV
Administration precautions: 
Toxicities: 
Lab surveillance: 

###

.idoralvancomycin
Antibiotic: Vancomycin
Indication: Clostridioides difficile infection
Duration: 10 days
Dosing: 10 mg/kg (max 125 mg/dose) four times daily
Route: PO
Administration precautions: 
Toxicities: 
Lab surveillance: none


